h; margin: 0px 0px 15px; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\\\\\"><strong style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(255,41,65); outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; outline-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; outline-color: invert; padding-right: 0px\\\\\">（三）中标候选人在投标文件中填报的项目业绩；</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/2em 微软雅黑; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px 0px 15px; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; outline-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; outline-color: invert; padding-right: 0px\\\\\">（四）提出异议的渠道和方式；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/2em 微软雅黑; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px 0px 15px; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; outline-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; outline-color: invert; padding-right: 0px\\\\\">（五）招标文件规定公示的其他内容。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/2em 微软雅黑; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px 0px 15px; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\\\\\"><strong style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\\\\\">第七条&nbsp;</strong>依法必须招标项目的公告和公示信息应当在国家电子招标投标公共服务平台或者项目所在地省级电子招标投标公共服务平台核验发布。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/2em 微软雅黑; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px 0px 15px; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; outline-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; outline-color: invert; padding-right: 0px\\\\\">各省、自治区、直辖市人民政府或其授权部门对本地区依法必须招标项目的公告和公示信息发布媒介另有规定的，前述信息在本地区指定发布媒介核验发布后，指定发布媒介应当同步交互至本地区省级电子招标投标公共服务平台或者国家电子招标投标公共服务平台发布。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/2em 微软雅黑; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px 0px 15px; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; outline-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; outline-color: invert; padding-right: 0px\\\\\">国家和省级电子招标投标公共服务平台，以及上款规定的其他指定发布媒介，以下统称&ldquo;发布媒介&rdquo;。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/2em 微软雅黑; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px 0px 15px; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\\\\\"><strong style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; outline-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; outline-color: invert; padding-right: 0px\\\\\">第八条</span></strong><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0,0,0); outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; outline-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; outline-color: invert; padding-right: 0px\\\\\">&nbsp;所有发布媒介应当与国家电子招标投标公共服务平台对接，按规定及时交互招标公告和公示信息，并与相应的公共资源交易平台实现信息共享。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/2em 微软雅黑; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px 0px 15px; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; outline-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; outline-color: invert; padding-right: 0px\\\\\">发布媒介的名称、网址、办公场所、联系方式等基本信息应当交互至国家电子招标投标公共服务平台向社会公布，并及时维护更新。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/2em 微软雅黑; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px 0px 15px; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\\\\\"><strong style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; outline-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; outline-color: invert; padding-right: 0px\\\\\">第九条&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0,0,0); outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; outline-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; outline-color: invert; padding-right: 0px\\\\\">拟发布的招标公告和公示信息文本应当由招标人或其招标代理机构的主要负责人或其授权的项目负责人签名并加盖公章。采用数据电文形式的，应当按照《中华人民共和国电子签名法》的规定进行电子签名。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/2em 微软雅黑; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px 0px 15px; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; outline-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; outline-color: invert; padding-right: 0px\\\\\">招标人或其招标代理机构发布资格预审公告、招标公告的，应当向发布媒介提供营业执照（或法人证书）、项目批准或备案文件的复印件等证明文件。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/2em 微软雅黑; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px 0px 15px; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; outline-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; outline-color: invert; padding-right: 0px\\\\\">招标人或其招标代理机构发布招标公告和公示信息，应当遵守招标投标法律法规关于时限的规定。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/2em 微软雅黑; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px 0px 15px; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\\\\\"><strong style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; outline-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; outline-color: invert; padding-right: 0px\\\\\">第十条&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0,0,0); outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; outline-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; outline-color: invert; padding-right: 0px\\\\\">核验发布媒介应当在收到招标公告和公示信息文本之日起 1 个工作日内发布。交互发布媒介应当在收到其他发布媒介交互的招标公告和公示信息起 1 小时内发布。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/2em 微软雅黑; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px 0px 15px; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; outline-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; outline-color: invert; padding-right: 0px\\\\\">招标人或其招标代理机构应当对其提供的招标公告和公示信息的真实性、准确性、合法性负责。核验发布媒介应当对所发布的招标公告和公示信息的及时性、完整性负责。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/2em 微软雅黑; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px 0px 15px; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; outline-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; outline-color: invert; padding-right: 0px\\\\\">发布媒介应当按照规定采取有效措施，确保发布招标公告和公示信息的数据电文不被篡改、不遗漏和至少 10 年内可追溯。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/2em 微软雅黑; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px 0px 15px; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\\\\\"><strong style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; outline-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; outline-color: invert; padding-right: 0px\\\\\">第十一条&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0,0,0); outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; outline-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; outline-color: invert; padding-right: 0px\\\\\">发布媒介应当通过专门栏目发布招标公告和公示信息，并提供信息归类和检索服务，对新发布的招标公告和公示信息作醒目标识，方便市场主体和社会公众查阅。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/2em 微软雅黑; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px 0px 15px; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; outline-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; outline-color: invert; padding-right: 0px\\\\\">发布媒介应当设置专门栏目，方便市场主体和社会公众就其招标公告和公示信息发布工作反映情况、提出意见，并及时反馈。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/2em 微软雅黑; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px 0px 15px; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\\\\\"><strong style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; outline-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; outline-color: invert; padding-right: 0px\\\\\">第十二条&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0,0,0); outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; outline-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; outline-color: invert; padding-right: 0px\\\\\">发布媒介应当免费提供依法必须招标项目的公告和公示信息发布服务，并允许社会公众和市场主体免费、及时查阅前述公告和公示的完整信息。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/2em 微软雅黑; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px 0px 15px; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\\\\\"><strong style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; outline-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; outline-color: invert; padding-right: 0px\\\\\">第十三条&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0,0,0); outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; outline-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; outline-color: invert; padding-right: 0px\\\\\">发布媒介应当实时统计招标公告和公示信息发布情况，及时向社会公布。国家电子招标投标公共服务平台应当实时统计全国招标公告和公示信息发布情况，及时向社会公布，并定期报送国家发展改革委。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/2em 微软雅黑; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px 0px 15px; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\\\\\"><strong style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; outline-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; outline-color: invert; padding-right: 0px\\\\\">第十四条&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0,0,0); outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; outline-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; outline-color: invert; padding-right: 0px\\\\\">除在发布媒介发布依法必须招标项目的招标公告和公示信息外，招标人或其招标代理机构也可以同步在其他媒介发布，并确保内容一致。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/2em 微软雅黑; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px 0px 15px; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; outline-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; outline-color: invert; padding-right: 0px\\\\\">其他媒介可以依法转载依法必须招标项目的公告和公示信息，但不得篡改，同时必须注明信息来源。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/2em 微软雅黑; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px 0px 15px; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\\\\\"><strong style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; outline-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; outline-color: invert; padding-right: 0px\\\\\">第十五条&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0,0,0); outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; outline-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; outline-color: invert; padding-right: 0px\\\\\">依法必须招标项目的公告和公示信息有下列情形之一的，潜在投标人或者投标人可以要求招标人或其招标代理机构予以改正、补充或调整：</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/2em 微软雅黑; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px 0px 15px; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; outline-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; outline-color: invert; padding-right: 0px\\\\\">（一）资格预审公告、招标公告载明的事项不符合本办法第五条规定，中标候选人公示载明的事项不符合本办法第六条规定；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/2em 微软雅黑; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px 0px 15px; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; outline-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; outline-color: invert; padding-right: 0px\\\\\">（二）在两家以上媒介发布的同一招标项目的公告和公示信息内容不一致；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/2em 微软雅黑; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px 0px 15px; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; outline-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; outline-color: invert; padding-right: 0px\\\\\">（三）公告和公示信息内容不符合法律法规规定。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/2em 微软雅黑; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px 0px 15px; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; outline-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; outline-color: invert; padding-right: 0px\\\\\">招标人或其招标代理机构应当认真核查，及时处理，并将处理结果告知提出意见的潜在投标人或者投标人。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/2em 微软雅黑; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px 0px 15px; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\\\\\"><strong style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; outline-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; outline-color: invert; padding-right: 0px\\\\\">第十六条&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0,0,0); outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; outline-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; outline-color: invert; padding-right: 0px\\\\\">任何单位和个人认为招标人或其代理机构在招标公告和公示信息发布活动中存在违法违规行为的，可以向有关行政监督部门投诉、举报；认为发布媒介在招标公告和公示信息发布活动中存在违法违规行为的，可以向相应的省级以上发展改革部门或者省级以上人民政府指定的其他部门投诉、举报。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/2em 微软雅黑; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px 0px 15px; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\\\\\"><strong style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; outline-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; outline-color: invert; padding-right: 0px\\\\\">第十七条&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0,0,0); outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; outline-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; outline-color: invert; padding-right: 0px\\\\\">招标人或其招标代理机构有下列行为之一的，由有关行政监督部门责令改正，并视情形依照《中华人民共和国招标投标法》第四十九条、第五十一条的规定处罚：</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/2em 微软雅黑; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px 0px 15px; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; outline-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; outline-color: invert; padding-right: 0px\\\\\">（一）依法必须公开招标项目不按照规定在指定媒介发布资格预审公告或者招标公告；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/2em 微软雅黑; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px 0px 15px; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; outline-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; outline-color: invert; padding-right: 0px\\\\\">（二）在不同媒介的发布的同一招标项目的资格预审公告或者招标公告的内容不一致，影响潜在投标人申请资格预审或者投标；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/2em 微软雅黑; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px 0px 15px; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; outline-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; outline-color: invert; padding-right: 0px\\\\\">（三）资格预审公告或者招标公告中有关获取资格预审文件或者招标文件的时限不符合招标投标法律法规规定；</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/2em 微软雅黑; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px 0px 15px; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; outline-style: none; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; outline-color: invert; padding-right: 0px\\\\\">（四）资格预审公告或者招标公告中以不合理的条件限制或者排斥潜在投标人。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100%; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; text-transform: none; color: rgb(62,62,62); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; font: 14px/2em 微软雅黑; padding-left: 0px; clear: both; margin: 0px 0px 15px; min-height: 1em; widows: 1; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0,0,0); padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; paddin